In below documentation pages it is not mentioned that if you have multiple workflows (associated to different issue types) configured for your Business project, then the board will fail:
- [Configuring Boards|https://confluence.atlassian.com/display/adminjiracloud/configuring+boards]
- [JIRA Core Labs|https://confluence.atlassian.com/jiracorecloud/jira-core-labs-800712865.html]


The above documentation pages only mention:
{quote}
A board will fail if:
There is more than one transition between two statuses going in the same direction i.e. transition A and transition B both go from status C to status D. 
{quote}


A board will also fail if you have different issue types associated to different workflows in your project.

